{{Infobox person | name = Per Lillo-Stenberg | image = 68511 Mette Lange-Nielsen og Per Lillo-Stenberg.jpg | caption = Lillo-Stenberg (left) with his wife [[Mette Lange-Nielsen]] in 1958 | birth_date = {{Birth date|1928|6|21|df=yes}} | birth_name = | birth_place = [[Oslo]], [[Norway]] | death_date = {{Death date and age|2014|3|27|1928|6|21|df=yes}} | death_place = [[Levanger]], Norway | nationality = [[Norway|Norwegian]] | occupation = Actor | spouse = [[Mette Lange-Nielsen]] | children = [[Lars Lillo-Stenberg]] }}
'''Per Lillo-Stenberg''' (21 June 1928 &ndash; 27 March 2014) was a [[Norwegians|Norwegian]] [[actor]]. His best known roles are in the [[movie]]s ''[[Olsenbanden gir seg aldri!]]'' (1981) and ''[[Olsenbandens siste stikk]]'' (1999). He was born in [[Oslo]]. He and his wife [[Mette Lange-Nielsen]] had a son, [[Lars Lillo-Stenberg]], a musician for [[deLillos]].
Lillo-Stenberg died after a short illness on 27 March 2014 in [[Levanger]]. He was 85.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vg.no/rampelys/per-lillo-stenberg-er-doed/a/10138691/|title=Per Lillo-Stenberg er død|publisher=''[[Verdens Gang]]''|date=28 March 2014|accessdate=30 March 2014|language=no}}</ref>
